lication of the blockchain.<ref name="ovpfaq">{{cite web |url=https://followmyvote.com/online-voting-platform-faqs/ |title=Online Voting Platform FAQ's |website=Follow My Vote |accessdate=7 December 2016 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027082454/https://followmyvote.com/online-voting-platform-faqs/ |archivedate=27 October 2016 |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.democracywithoutborders.org/de/4625/reimagining-democracy-what-if-votes-were-a-crypto-currency/|title=Reimagining Democracy: What if votes were a crypto-currency?|last=Chandra|first=Prabhul|website=democracywithoutborders.org|access-date=2018-02-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205184846/https://www.democracywithoutborders.org/de/4625/reimagining-democracy-what-if-votes-were-a-crypto-currency/|archivedate=5 February 2018|df=dmy-all}}</ref> 

